simple-FileManager-using-NSFileManager-Tables-custom-cells-and-NSOperation
============================================================================

API illustrates blocks, work with NSFileManager, NSOperations and custom cells. 

Key features of the FileManager app:

- Practicing with NSFileManager - the ability to create directories
- The ability to delete files and directories
- Sorting of the files and folders: from the top are the folders, sorted by descending name, the files are below, sorted by size
- Hidden files are not shown in the file manager
- The file size is shown in detailedTextField of each file's cell
- Recursive calculation of each folder size using NSOperation in the background thread